I"π<p>Ver la versi√≥n actual de node:</p>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>node <span class="nt">-v</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Instalar dependencias de desarrollo:</p>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>npm <span class="nb">install </span>nombre_paquete <span class="nt">-D</span><span class="sb">`</span>

O versi√≥n extendida:

<span class="sb">`</span><span class="nv">$ </span>npm <span class="nb">install </span>nombre_paquete <span class="nt">--save-dev</span><span class="sb">`</span>

Comprobar si existen versiones m√°s actuales de los paquetes instalados:

<span class="sb">`</span><span class="nv">$ </span>npm outdate<span class="sb">`</span>

Actualizar todos los paquetes:

<span class="sb">`</span><span class="nv">$ </span>npm update<span class="sb">`</span>

Actualizar solo el paquete nombrado:

<span class="sb">`</span><span class="nv">$ </span>npm update nombre_paquete<span class="sb">`</span>

Desinstalar el paquete nombrado:

<span class="sb">`</span><span class="nv">$ </span>npm uninstall nombre_paquete<span class="sb">`</span>

Revisar vulnerabilidades de seguridad:

<span class="sb">`</span><span class="nv">$ </span>npm audit<span class="sb">`</span>

Corregir vulnerabilidades de seguridad:

<span class="sb">`</span><span class="nv">$ </span>npm audit fix<span class="sb">`</span>

Actualizar npm globalmente a la √∫ltima versi√≥n:

<span class="sb">`</span><span class="nv">$ </span>npm <span class="nb">install </span>npm@latest <span class="nt">-g</span><span class="sb">`</span>

Eliminar node_modules de tu proyecto y volver a instalar las dependencias de nuevo:

<span class="sb">```</span>shell
<span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">rm</span> <span class="nt">-rf</span> node_modules
<span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">rm</span> <span class="nt">-rf</span> package-lock.json
<span class="nv">$ </span>npm cache clean <span class="nt">-f</span>
<span class="nv">$ </span>npm <span class="nb">install</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

